/*
    ctrl + E ===> open Recent Files
    ctrl + NumPad-1 : show the current file on project view, active select file in Project view
    ctrl + shift + f  ===> search on file/ find in files
    ctrl + shift + f12 ===> maximize the current page, the editor/ hide all windows
    ctrl + w ===> extend selection
    ctrl + shift + arrow keys up/down ===> Move selection
    ctrl + alt + l ===> Reformat Code
    ctrl + shift + N ===> Open search EveryWhere plane
    double ctrl ===> open Run Anything
    ctrl + shift + j ===> join the multiline string lines together
    alt + shift + clickMouse ===> can select different place and change it all together
    alt + J ===> Add selection for next Occurrence(select a Word multiple time in the code)
    shift + F6 ===> Rename
    Ctrl+Shift+\ ===>	Remove Block Comment
*/
